<div class="container">
    <div><h1>Alert.js</h1></div>
    <br />
    <div class="bg-success row" style="margin-bottom:15px;">
        <h3 class="col-md-12">基本範例</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 alert alert-warning alert-dismissible fade in" role="alert">
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">
                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                <span class="sr-only">Close</span>
            </button>
            <strong>測試</strong>Prime Minister Lars Lokke Rasmussen said he was concerned that "democratic principles are under great pressure" in Turkey.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <strong>監聽事件</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <table class="table table-hover">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th style="width:10%">事件</th>
                        <th style="width:90%">說明</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            close.bs.alert
                        </td>
                        <td>
                            當<code>close</code>執行個體方法被呼叫時觸發。
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            closed.bs.alert
                        </td>
                        <td>
                            當警告訊息已經在使用者面前關閉完成（且 CSS 轉場效果已經完成），此事件會被觸發。
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <blockquote class="col-md-12 bg-warning">
            <ul>
                <li>在關閉紐上加入data-dismiss="alert"、對應的外層div加入.alert即可</li>
                <li>此關閉功能會將整個元素移除</li>
                <li>透過加入<code>.fade</code>跟<code>.in</code>才會有動畫效果</li>
            </ul>
        </blockquote>
    </div>
